request.description:
* Creating a new Person using POST /api/v1.0/persons API
* localhost:8080/api/v1.0/persons/
* Example: {"firstName": "Gonzalo", "lastName":"Martinez"}

* Updating a Person using PUT /api/v1.0/persons/{personId} API
* localhost:8080/api/v1.0/persons/1
* Example: {"firstName": "Frederic", "lastName":"Chopin"}
